1. Dolphin, Download
 
Dolphin is on GitHub.
 
  http://github.com/nickeo/Dolphin/
 
Dowload it and point browser to index.php. Update pagespecific constants in config files. 

There is currently no stable version of Dolphin.


2. Dolphin, A template for websites
 
Dolphin is to be a simple and clean but powerful webtemplate.

3. Dolphin - why
 
Dolphin is the result of my attempts to learn php at BTH.
 
 
4. Dolphin, The name
 
I like dolphins. It's as simple as that.


